OL,3,CBritish Steel consults people on
OL,4,CTeesside over 'green' electric arc
OL,5,Cfurnace plans
OL,7,FBritish Steel has held a consultation
OL,8,Fevent in Redcar to explain to people
OL,9,Fhow its #1.25 billion plans to build
OL,10,Ftwo electric arc furnaces in
OL,11,FScunthorpe and Redcar will help the
OL,12,Fcompany become cleaner, greener and
OL,13,Fmore sustainable.
OL,15,FThe plans involve replacing the
OL,16,Ftraditional blast furnaces, which
OL,17,Frelied on coal as a source of fuel,
OL,18,Fwith the electric arc furnaces, which
OL,19,Fuse renewably generated electricity to
OL,20,Fmelt the raw steel.
